[SN]TITLE[SN]
Gone: Newsround special programme on coping with death

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Watch Gone, Newsround's special programme on coping with death.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Presented by Barney Harwood, this Newsround special explores the issue of bereavement and the effect it has on children's lives.
It tells the story of four children, all of whom have lost someone they love.
